=================================================================
  HOW TO ADD THESE IN VERCEL:
=================================================================

1. Go to: https://vercel.com/dashboard
2. Click on your "bookster" project
3. Click "Settings" tab
4. Click "Environment Variables" in the left sidebar
5. For each variable above:
   - Click "Add New"
   - Enter the Name
   - Paste the Value
   - Check all three boxes: Production, Preview, Development
   - Click "Save"

6. After adding all three variables:
   - Go to "Deployments" tab
   - Click on the latest deployment
   - Click the "..." menu (three dots)
   - Click "Redeploy"
   - UNCHECK "Use existing Build Cache"
   - Click "Redeploy"

7. Wait 2-5 minutes for deployment to complete

8. Test at: https://booksterisu.vercel.app/login

